But young Maurizio was head over heels for Patrizia, and his

00:06:38.328 --> 00:06:42.718
father had to resort to more extreme measures to break the pair up.

00:06:43.678 --> 00:06:48.798
He disinherited his son, cutting Maurizio off from the family company and money.

00:06:49.468 --> 00:06:51.198
But this still did not work.

00:06:52.288 --> 00:06:58.558
As the wedding drew closer, Rodolfo Gucci even asked the cardinal of Milan to put a stop to it.

00:06:59.618 --> 00:07:06.438
It was no use and the couple married in 1972 with no members of the Gucci family in attendance.

00:07:07.728 --> 00:07:12.098
But luck was about to turn for the new Mr and Mrs Gucci.

