00:16:30.663 --> 00:16:35.733
This ate away at Gucci’s bottom line, and the finances were in the red.

00:16:36.643 --> 00:16:42.513
Investcorp no longer trusted Maurizio to run the company, and they wanted to buy him out too.

00:16:43.893 --> 00:16:49.573
