00:17:21.763 --> 00:17:25.833
Unfortunately for him, no amount of loans or dodgy dealings could

00:17:25.833 --> 00:17:31.473
save him, and in 1993 he finally sold his half of Gucci to Investcorp.

00:17:32.453 --> 00:17:37.213
